itemLabel: Henry Dalziel, 1st Baron Dalziel of Kirkcaldy

wikipedia_page.main: James Henry Dalziel, 1st Baron Dalziel of Kirkcaldy PC (24 April 1868 – 15 July 1935), known as Sir Henry Dalziel, Bt, between 1918 and 1921, was a British newspaper proprietor, Liberal politician and supporter of David Lloyd George.
